<h2 style="color: #2C5234; margin-bottom: 20px;">Payment Confirmation</h2>

<p>Hello {{recipientName}},</p>

<div style="background-color: #f5f6f7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h3 style="color: #2C5234; margin-top: 0;">Payment Details</h3>
    
    <div style="margin-top: 15px;">
        <p><strong>Amount Paid:</strong> ${{amount}}</p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{date}}</p>
        <p><strong>Payment Method:</strong> {{paymentMethod}}</p>
        <p><strong>Confirmation Number:</strong> {{confirmationNumber}}</p>
    </div>
</div>

<p>A receipt for this payment has been attached to this email for your records.</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
    <a href="{{paymentHistoryUrl}}" class="button" style="font-size: 16px;">
        View Payment History
    </a>
</div>

<p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 30px;">
    If you're having trouble with the button above, you can copy and paste this link into your browser:<br>
    <a href="{{paymentHistoryUrl}}" style="color: #2C5234;">{{paymentHistoryUrl}}</a>
</p>

<hr style="border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #eee; margin: 20px 0;">

<p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
    This is an automated notification from Summit Ridge HOA. You can update your email preferences at any time in your 
    <a href="{{preferencesUrl}}" style="color: #2C5234;">account settings</a>.
</p>